    "endTime": 299.89,
    "text": "[LAUGHS]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 300.39,
    "endTime": 301.74199999999996,
    "text": "Oh, my god."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 301.742,
    "endTime": 307.93,
    "text": "OK, Ellen, I want to try an\nexercise with 24 Rubik's Cubes."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 307.93,
    "endTime": 308.47,
    "text": "All right?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 308.47,
    "endTime": 311.10400000000004,
    "text": "So when I was in college,\nto get my mind focused,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 311.104,
    "endTime": 313.27,
    "text": "I'd write down what I was\nthinking on this notebook."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 313.27,
    "endTime": 317.44,
    "text": "For example, I have a\nRubik's Cube, girls."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 317.44,
    "endTime": 318.34,
    "text": "[LAUGHTER]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 318.34,
    "endTime": 321.72999999999996,
    "text": "Lamborghini, a bench\npress, Pac-Man."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 321.73,
    "endTime": 322.66,
    "text": "Mm-hmm?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 322.66,
    "endTime": 324.19,
    "text": "Can you hold the notebook\nin your hand like this?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 324.19,
    "endTime": 324.76,
    "text": "Yep."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 324.76,
    "endTime": 325.03499999999997,
    "text": "And then--"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 325.035,
    "endTime": 325.19,
    "text": "Yeah."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 325.19,
    "endTime": 325.995,
    "text": "--put my hand like that?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 325.995,
    "endTime": 326.495,
    "text": "Yeah."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 326.495,
    "endTime": 327.43,
    "text": "And close your eyes."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 327.43,
    "endTime": 328.88800000000003,
    "text": "And riffle up the\nback of the book."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 328.888,
    "endTime": 329.58,
    "text": "Mm-hmm."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 329.58,
    "endTime": 330.83,
    "text": "And when you want, stop."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 330.83,
    "endTime": 331.33,
    "text": "OK."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 331.33,
    "endTime": 331.81,
    "text": "And lift up."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 331.81,
    "endTime": 332.14,
    "text": "And look."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 332.14,
    "endTime": 332.65,
    "text": "And remember."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 332.65,
    "endTime": 332.95,
    "text": "OK?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 332.95,
    "endTime": 333.21,
    "text": "Got it?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 333.21,
    "endTime": 333.58,
    "text": "OK."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 333.58,
    "endTime": 334.15,
    "text": "Yep."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 334.15,
    "endTime": 334.48999999999995,
    "text": "Got it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 334.49,
    "endTime": 335.06,
    "text": "And close the back of it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 335.06,
    "endTime": 335.15,
    "text": "Yep."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 335.15,
    "endTime": 336.21999999999997,
    "text": "And I'll take it back."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 336.22,
    "endTime": 336.38000000000005,
    "text": "Mm-hmm."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 336.38,
    "endTime": 337.48,
    "text": "And we're done with this."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 337.48,
    "endTime": 338.896,
    "text": "Now, we're going\nto try something."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 338.896,
    "endTime": 340.584,
    "text": "It's called speed\nmixing and stacking."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 340.584,
    "endTime": 342.25,
    "text": "You're going to mix\nthese Rubik's Cubes."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 342.25,
    "endTime": 343.25,
    "text": "I'm going to stack them."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 343.25,
    "endTime": 346.1,
    "text": "But this entire time, I want\nyou to focus on your word."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 346.1,
    "endTime": 346.6,
    "text": "OK?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 346.6,
    "endTime": 347.02000000000004,
    "text": "Are you ready?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 347.02,
    "endTime": 348.83,
    "text": "Like, mix them up and\nthen hand them to you?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 348.83,
    "endTime": 348.87199999999996,
    "text": "Yeah."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 348.872,
    "endTime": 348.914,
    "text": "Yeah."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 348.914,
    "endTime": 349.03999999999996,
    "text": "Mix them up."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 349.04,
    "endTime": 349.3,
    "text": "OK."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 349.3,
    "endTime": 350.466,
    "text": "And so, OK, OK, mix them up."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 350.466,
    "endTime": 351.01,
    "text": "Let's go now."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 351.01,
    "endTime": 351.51,
    "text": "OK."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 351.51,
    "endTime": 352.34,
    "text": "Go ahead."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 352.34,
    "endTime": 352.84,
    "text": "OK."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 352.84,
    "endTime": 353.36999999999995,
    "text": "Oh, wow."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 353.37,
    "endTime": 355.18,
    "text": "No, no, no, you're going\nway too fast for me."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 355.18,
    "endTime": 355.53000000000003,
    "text": "That's OK."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 355.53,
    "endTime": 356.015,
    "text": "[LAUGHS]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 356.015,
    "endTime": 356.257,
    "text": "All right."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 356.257,
    "endTime": 356.5,
    "text": "Keep going."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 356.5,
    "endTime": 357.11,
    "text": "All right."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 357.11,
    "endTime": 358.03000000000003,
    "text": "[LAUGHTER]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 358.657,
    "endTime": 359.74,
    "text": "Now try to keep on mixing."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 359.74,
    "endTime": 360.38,
    "text": "Keep on mixing."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 360.38,
    "endTime": 361.2,
    "text": "I'm stacking."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 361.2,
    "endTime": 362.881,
    "text": "Ellen, have you\ndone this before?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 362.881,
    "endTime": 363.38,
    "text": "Yeah."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 363.38,
    "endTime": 363.65,
    "text": "Oh."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 363.65,
    "endTime": 364.078,
    "text": "What have you done?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 364.078,
    "endTime": 364.93399999999997,
    "text": "Every day."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 364.934,
    "endTime": 365.72,
    "text": "[LAUGHTER]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 366.22,
    "endTime": 367.81,
    "text": "So this is-- we're\nalmost-- we've"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 367.81,
    "endTime": 370.61,
    "text": "done the first-- essentially,\nthe first two layers."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 370.61,
    "endTime": 372.98,
    "text": "And we're about to do the\nother-- oh, thank you, Ellen."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 372.98,
    "endTime": 373.48,
    "text": "Let's see."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 373.48,
    "endTime": 375.01,
    "text": "This one can go right here."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 375.01,
    "endTime": 376.90999999999997,
    "text": "And this one can go right here."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 376.91,
    "endTime": 378.03000000000003,
    "text": "And I'll take this one."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 378.03,
    "endTime": 379.0,
    "text": "Actually, this\none doesn't look--"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 379.0,
    "endTime": 380.53,
    "text": "OK, this one could\ngo right here."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 380.53,
    "endTime": 381.72999999999996,
    "text": "Keep focusing on your word."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 381.73,
    "endTime": 382.23,
    "text": "Right."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 382.23,
    "endTime": 383.47,
    "text": "We're almost halfway done."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 383.47,
    "endTime": 383.79,
    "text": "Right."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 383.79,
    "endTime": 384.38,
    "text": "And the idea's simple."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 384.38,
    "endTime": 386.31,
    "text": "Don't let any other thought\ncome into your mind."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 386.31,
    "endTime": 386.809,
    "text": "OK?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 386.809,
    "endTime": 388.64000000000004,
    "text": "Just think of your word."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 388.64,
    "endTime": 389.14,
    "text": "All right."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 389.14,
    "endTime": 390.62,
    "text": "And oh, this one too."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 390.62,
    "endTime": 392.44,
    "text": "And we'll try this."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 392.44,
    "endTime": 395.3,
    "text": "Do you see what's kind of like--"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 395.3,
    "endTime": 395.8,
    "text": "yeah."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 395.8,
    "endTime": 396.40000000000003,
    "text": "You do see it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 396.4,
    "endTime": 396.9,
    "text": "Right?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 396.9,
    "endTime": 397.59,
    "text": "You do?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 397.59,
    "endTime": 398.21,
    "text": "Yeah."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 398.21,
    "endTime": 398.71,
    "text": "It's a--"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 398.71,
    "endTime": 399.79999999999995,
    "text": "I think so because--"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 399.8,
    "endTime": 400.02000000000004,
    "text": "Yeah, OK."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 400.02,
    "endTime": 400.37,
    "text": "OK."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 400.37,
    "endTime": 401.32,
    "text": "I'll tell you in a minute."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 401.32,
    "endTime": 401.59,
    "text": "All right."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 401.59,
    "endTime": 402.089,
    "text": "So--"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 402.089,
    "endTime": 402.82,
    "text": "[LAUGHTER]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 403.52,
    "endTime": 404.02,
    "text": "Perfect."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 404.02,
    "endTime": 404.853,
    "text": "We'll take this one."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 404.853,
    "endTime": 406.735,
    "text": "And I am quite a perfectionist."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 406.735,
    "endTime": 408.27000000000004,
    "text": "So I'm going to take my time."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 408.27,
    "endTime": 409.69,
    "text": "Can you mix this\none again for me?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 409.69,
    "endTime": 410.96,
    "text": "Thank you."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 410.96,
    "endTime": 411.46,
    "text": "Let's see."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 411.46,
    "endTime": 414.15999999999997,
    "text": "This one can go right here."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 414.16,
    "endTime": 416.39000000000004,
    "text": "This one right here."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 416.39,
    "endTime": 420.55,
    "text": "And we'll take these here."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 420.55,
    "endTime": 423.12,
